cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

The paper discusses the mapping component of an end-to-end system for autonomous vehicles, which involves computer vision (CV) techniques for sign and lane detection, robotics (RO) for autonomous vehicle navigation, machine learning (LG and AI) for offline clustering and bundle adjustment, and graphics (GR) for constructing 3D maps. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV, followed by cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, and cs.GR.
